# RAG System Setup and Usage Guide

This guide provides instructions for setting up and running a simple Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system.

website - ecommerce - example:
https://monorimspain.com/

## 1. Setup

### 1.1 Create and Activate Virtual Environment

It's highly recommended to use a virtual environment to manage dependencies for your project.

```bash
python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate
```

### 1.2 Install Required Libraries

Install all necessary Python libraries using pip.

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```


